data.description: This home offers a 2.75% assumable mortgage making it very affordable! Step inside to this single-story 4-bedroom, plus office, 3-bath home. The triple split floorplan ensures privacy for everyone as well as optimal comfort and functionality. It has wood floors throughout (no carpet!,) real wood cabinets, gas cooking and granite countertops, all exuding quality&style.Retreat to your tranquil master suite, complete with a spa-like ensuite bathroom and a generous walk-in closet.The large covered patio is a haven for outdoor living. Neighborhood pool, park and walking trails are a short stroll away plus Topgolf, Costco, Target  and dining within a mile!  Flood insurance not required.  Preferred lender also offering other loan options & closing cost assistance.
